# Google reCAPTCHA v2 Site Key (public)
# Get this from https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin
# IMPORTANT: This is the SITE KEY (public), NOT the SECRET KEY
# The SECRET KEY should be configured in your EmailJS template settings only
# Example: VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=6LcAOY0sAAAAABqFjpb-9KK5jOb905i7ar7iHVoJ
VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_recaptcha_v2_site_key_here
